NAME
    gcloud beta network-connectivity hubs groups - manage Network Connectivity
        Center groups

SYNOPSIS
    gcloud beta network-connectivity hubs groups COMMAND [GCLOUD_WIDE_FLAG ...]

DESCRIPTION
    (BETA) Manage Network Connectivity Center groups.

GCLOUD WIDE FLAGS
    These flags are available to all commands: --help.

    Run $ gcloud help for details.

COMMANDS
    COMMAND is one of the following:

     add-iam-policy-binding
        (BETA) Add an IAM policy binding to the IAM policy of a group resource.

     describe
        (BETA) Describe a group.

     get-iam-policy
        (BETA) Get the IAM policy for a group resource.

     list
        (BETA) List groups.

     remove-iam-policy-binding
        (BETA) Remove an IAM policy binding from the IAM policy of a group
        resource.

     set-iam-policy
        (BETA) Set the IAM policy of a group resource.

     update
        (BETA) Update a group.

NOTES
    This command is currently in beta and might change without notice. This
    variant is also available:

        $ gcloud network-connectivity hubs groups

